      <h1 class='title'>Departmental Expenditure</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1688WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1688ws' title='Col. 1688WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1688WS' name='column_1688ws' href='#column_1688ws' rel='bookmark'>1688WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_228'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/viscount-thurso' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_228' title='Link to this speech by Viscount  Thurso' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/viscount-thurso" title="Viscount  Thurso">John Thurso</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Scotland how much his Department has spent on electricity use for each year since 1997. [186655]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_229'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-anne-mcguire' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_229' title='Link to this speech by Mrs Anne McGuire' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mrs-anne-mcguire" title="Mrs Anne McGuire">Mrs. McGuire</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">The Scotland Office was established on 1 July 1999.</p><p>Since that date electricity costs of the Scotland Office and Office of the Advocate-General are as follows:</p><p>
          <table>
          <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td><span class="italic">&#x00A3;</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1999&#x2013;2000<sup>1</sup></td>
          <td>11,855</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2000&#x2013;01</td>
          <td>22,807</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2001&#x2013;02</td>
          <td>19,526</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2002&#x2013;03</td>
          <td>28.439</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2003&#x2013;04</td>
          <td>23,703</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>1</sup>Part year.</td>
          </tr>
          </table>
          </p><p>The information relates to buildings where the Scotland Office are major occupiers. Costs relating to buildings shared with the Scottish Executive are not separately identifiable.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_230'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/viscount-thurso' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_230' title='Link to this speech by Viscount  Thurso' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/viscount-thurso" title="Viscount  Thurso">John Thurso</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Scotland how much his Department has spent on water and sewerage services in each year since 1997. [186656]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_231'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-anne-mcguire' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_231' title='Link to this speech by Mrs Anne McGuire' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mrs-anne-mcguire" title="Mrs Anne McGuire">Mrs. McGuire</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">The Scotland Office was established on 1 July 1999.</p><p>Since that date water and sewerage costs of the Scotland Office and Office of the Advocate-General are as follows:</p><p>
          <table>
          <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td><span class="italic">&#x00A3;</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1999&#x2013;2000<sup>1</sup></td>
          <td>1,067</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2000&#x2013;01</td>
          <td>3,656</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2001&#x2013;02</td>
          <td>4,221</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2002&#x2013;03</td>
          <td>7,018</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2003&#x2013;04</td>
          <td>11,699</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>1</sup>Part year.</td>
          </tr>
          </table>
          </p><p>The information relates to buildings where the Scotland Office are major occupiers. Costs relating to buildings shared with the Scottish Executive are not separately identifiable.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
